Package: netdata-lsi-hba-temp
Architecture: all
Depends: netdata, systemd, bash, grep, coreutils, lsi-hba-temp
Description: Netdata external plugin for lsi-hba-temp journal output
 Reads lsi-hba-temp journal/syslog payloads and publishes LSI/Broadcom HBA
 temperature and state charts to Netdata.
